    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      727.75,
      524.77,
      759.39
    ],
    "text": "Suspect Arrested for Aiding and Abetting a Money Laundering Offence \u2013 Computer Crime Investigation Division, North Western Province",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      32.13,
      526.06,
      95.93
    ],
    "text": "The North Western Provincial Computer Crime Investigation Unit commenced an investigation following a complaint regarding an online investment fraud in which the complainant was induced to transfer money under the pretext of participating in an online business venture.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      110.51,
      505.95,
      158.21
    ],
    "text": "During the investigation, officers arrested a suspect on 13.07.2026 for allegedly assisting in the laundering of Rs. 824,004 out of the total Rs. 10,245,280 fraudulently obtained from the complainant.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      172.79,
      424.33,
      188.33
    ],
    "text": "The suspect is a 37-year-old resident of Thawalantenna.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      202.91,
      498.64,
      266.72
    ],
    "text": "The suspect is scheduled to be produced before the Galgamuwa Magistrate's Court on 14.07.2026. Further investigations are being conducted by the Computer Crime Investigation Unit of the Criminal Investigation Department, North Western Province.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
